    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. The engine and transmission are operational and have been regularly serviced, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage typical for its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dents, and the interior shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery and fading on the dashboard. While it lacks the polish of a newer model, it is mechanically sound and ready for the road.",
