    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a dependable driving experience. While the exterior and interior are clean and well-kept, you may find a few minor scratches and light interior wear typical of a pre-owned car. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
